OL,6,FA driver who threw his dashcam into
OL,7,Fanother car after killing a great-
OL,8,Fgrandmother as she crossed the road
OL,9,Fhas had his prison sentence increased.
OL,11,FTasham Mahmood fatally injured 69-year-
OL,12,Fold Carol Andrew when he collided with
OL,13,Fher on White Lee Road in Heckmondwike,
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire, in July 2021.
OL,16,FHe threw his dashcam into the car of a
OL,17,Fmotorist who stopped at the scene, but
OL,18,Fthe device was later recovered.
