OL,3,CMore jail time for driver who ditched
OL,4,Cdashcam after killing great gran
OL,6,FMahmood, 34, was jailed for four years
OL,7,Fin April this year, but the case was
OL,8,Freferred to the Court of Appeal by the
OL,9,FSolicitor General, on the grounds that
OL,10,Fit was "unduly lenient".
OL,12,FThree senior judges have now increased
OL,13,Fthe sentence to six years and four
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FIn their judgement Lord Justice Singh,
OL,17,FMrs Justice May and Mrs Justice
OL,18,FThornton said Ms Andrew's death was
OL,19,F"tragic and needless", and offered
OL,20,F"sincere sympathy" to her family.
