OL,3,CMore jail time for driver who ditched
OL,4,Cdashcam after killing great gran
OL,6,FThey said dashcam footage showed the
OL,7,F"appalling nature of the offender's
OL,8,Fdriving over a sustained period of
OL,9,Ftime".
OL,11,FLord Justice Singh said: "The offender
OL,12,Fdrove dangerously and without regard
OL,13,Fto the safety of other road users. He
OL,14,Fperformed dangerous manoeuvres."
OL,16,FMs Andrew was walking home with her
OL,17,Fdog as she crossed White Lee Road in
OL,18,FHeckmondwike when she was struck by
OL,19,FMahmood's Seat Leon.
