OL,4,Cdashcam after killing great gran
OL,6,FHe had overtaken several vehicles,
OL,7,Fdrove through three red lights and
OL,8,Freached speeds of more than 80mph
OL,9,Fbefore hitting her.
OL,11,FThe mother-of-two, grandmother-of-four
OL,12,Fand great-grandmother-of-one suffered
OL,13,Fmultiple injuries and died at the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FMahmood admitted causing Ms Andrew's
OL,17,Fdeath in January and was sentenced at
OL,18,FLeeds Crown Court in April.
