OL,6,FThe Court of Appeal heard Mahmood was
OL,7,Fdriving home after being told his
OL,8,Fbrother was "seriously unwell", with
OL,9,Fhis sibling dying later that night.
OL,11,FHis barristers said "mercy" was a
OL,12,F"necessary feature" of the case, and
OL,13,Fthat the sentence should not be
OL,14,Fincreased.
OL,16,FHelen Chapman, for Mahmood, said: "I
OL,17,Fwould invite the court to be slow to
OL,18,Fdisturb the sentence of a judge who
OL,19,Fwas in the best possible position to
OL,20,Fweigh up all the relevant features."
